snippet.title: Oh no ! more lemmings (Macintosh game 1992)
snippet.description:
It is an Apple Macintosh version of Oh no! more Lemmings.
The resolution is higher and graphics is better than such other version of it as MS-DOS, Amiga, Atari ST and so forth.
The background music is same with other versions but sound quality is better than them.

Accordingly, if you've played other version Lemmings, you can play it without any problems.
